{"tid":2324882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版N號房｜ 7男被捕涉串謀賣淫 《蘋果》獨家曝光近半年 警未提主腦落網與否","createTime":"2020-12-14T09:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T14:24:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4b6c1ca90f0657bf0dd2fac044f42929969c33","tid":2324882,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:06:55.000Z","msg":"今年6月中《蘋果》獨家揭發，有不法之徒以威逼利誘手段，迫使無辜市民上酒店房接受性侵，過程更被拍片轉售，儼如韓國「N號房」事件翻版。報道刊登後全城震驚，至今日，警方終表示就案件拘捕7名男子，涉嫌「串謀控制他人而目的在於使他與人非法性交或賣淫」罪，惟集團主腦「阿希」落網與否，警未有提及。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201214/6XUEUNXEHZGW3HSHFVNBFIDPN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201214%2F6XUEUNXEHZGW3HSHFVNBFIDPN4%2F&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725Mls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=d840f581\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201214%2F6XUEUNXEHZGW3HSHFVNBFIDPN4%2F&h=a437abe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201214/6XUEUNXEHZGW3HSHFVNBFIDPN4/</a>"},{"pid":"d261a40ead6409bde58a92c2116980f130830d66","tid":2324882,"uid":376103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"你係呀希？"},{"pid":"be2c55fbc229020ea9b067ed4b84091718435c45","tid":2324882,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965852d32e6f20306d8b275cf2570c5ce254c7e7","tid":2324882,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,